title: The Mexican flag is turning into a symbol of destruction.

author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, chaos erupts in Los Angeles as riots break out to protest the deportation of criminal aliens. It’s the “Summer of Love” 2.0 — it could get a lot worse, if the terrorists aren’t subdued and brought to justice. Also, the Elon vs. Trump feud seems to have died down after just a day or two. But, I have a few thoughts on the subject. And Simone Biles launches a vicious attack against Riley Gaines on behalf of men who want to play women’s sports.
